## Maintenance Checklist

### When to Update Rules

Update rules when:
- [ ] New patterns emerge in codebase
- [ ] Team agrees on different approach
- [ ] Technology/framework updates change best practices
- [ ] Rules cause confusion or questions
- [ ] You find yourself repeating same code review comments

## Quick Start Template

Copy this template for new rule files:

````markdown
---
description: [Brief description]
globs: [file patterns]
---

